{"title":"Gershon","link":"/en/wol/d/r1/lp-e/1200001663","html":"<span id=\"page926\" class=\"pageNum\" data-no=\"926\" data-before-text=\"926\"></span><strong>GERSHON</strong>(Ger&#x2B9;shon) [An Alien Resident There].The first listed of Levi&#x2019;s three sons. Gershon&#x2019;s descendants were called Gershonites and &#x201C;sons of Gershon.&#x201D; (<a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200001663/0/0\" data-bid=\"1-1\" class=\"b\">Ex 6:16;</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200001663/0/1\" data-bid=\"1-2\" class=\"b\"> Nu 3:17,</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200001663/0/2\" data-bid=\"1-3\" class=\"b\"> 21;</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200001663/0/3\" data-bid=\"1-4\" class=\"b\"> 7:7;</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200001663/0/4\" data-bid=\"1-5\" class=\"b\"> 26:57;</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200001663/0/5\" data-bid=\"1-6\" class=\"b\"> Jos 21:6,</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200001663/0/6\" data-bid=\"1-7\" class=\"b\"> 27;</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200001663/0/7\" data-bid=\"1-8\" class=\"b\"> 1Ch 6:1;</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200001663/0/8\" data-bid=\"1-9\" class=\"b\"> 23:6</a>) He is also called Gershom. (<a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200001663/1/0\" data-bid=\"2-1\" class=\"b\">1Ch 6:16, 17,</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200001663/1/1\" data-bid=\"2-2\" class=\"b\"> 20,</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200001663/1/2\" data-bid=\"2-3\" class=\"b\"> 43,</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200001663/1/3\" data-bid=\"2-4\" class=\"b\"> 62,</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200001663/1/4\" data-bid=\"2-5\" class=\"b\"> 71;</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200001663/1/5\" data-bid=\"2-6\" class=\"b\"> 15:7</a>) Gershon&#x2019;s sons were Libni (evidently called Ladan at <a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200001663/2/0\" data-bid=\"3-1\" class=\"b\">1Ch 23:7;</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200001663/2/1\" data-bid=\"3-2\" class=\"b\"> 26:21</a>) and Shimei.<wbr>&#x2014;<a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200001663/3/0\" data-bid=\"4-1\" class=\"b\">Ex 6:17;</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200001663/3/1\" data-bid=\"4-2\" class=\"b\"> Nu 3:18;</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200001663/3/2\" data-bid=\"4-3\" class=\"b\"> 1Ch 6:17,</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200001663/3/3\" data-bid=\"4-4\" class=\"b\">&#xA0;20</a>."}